If you wish to return to the UK from Angola, keep up to date with information from your tour operator, transport or accommodation provider on the impact on any existing travel plans.
Many visitors from the UK travel to Angola via South Africa. South Africa has put in place travel restrictions on individuals from countries affected by coronavirus, including the United Kingdom. Keep up to date with FCO travel advice for South Africa for information on South African entry requirements, and consult your nearest South African High Commission.
Further information
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
